These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: purple, emerald, amber, fuchsia, aquamarine, lilac, brown
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cycling, biathlon, soccer, surfing, handball, tennis, basketball
 1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person who's sport is handball is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 3. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 5. the person who likes amber is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who's sport is cycling##1
 8. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
11. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Color           | aquamarine | fuchsia | emerald | amber | purple | lilac | brown |
| Sport   | cycling    | handball   | surfing      | tennis | soccer    | biathlon    | basketball         |

