.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: tennis, skateboarding, cricket, volleyball, ice-hockey, sailing, skiing
There are 7 different favourite colors: coral, mauve, turquise, lilac, lavender, black, ebony
 1. the person who likes lavender is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 3. the person who likes black is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 7. the person who likes lavender is in the middle##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Sport          | tennis | skateboarding | ice-hockey | volleyball | sailing | skiing | cricket |
| Color   | mauve      | turquise   | lilac   | lavender      | coral       | ebony       | black     |

