.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, art-deco, townhouse, modern, farmhouse, victorian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: soccer, skiing, cycling, lacrosse, climbing, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the modern house##1
 2. the modern house is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the victorian house##1
 4. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 5. the person who's sport is soccer is the modern house##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the farmhouse house is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
11. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in the middle##1
12. the victorian house is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| House   | cape-cod | modern     | art-deco  | farmhouse       | gothic-revival       | victorian  | townhouse   |
| Sport    | water-polo  | soccer | weightlifting | lacrosse | skiing | cycling | climbing |

