.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: time-travel, family, adventure, horror, martial-arts, fantasy, drama
There 7 different types of food: corn, tomato, pepper, radish, pumpkin, plum, peas
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person eating tomato##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 3. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 4. the person eating corn is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating pumpkin##1
10. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
11. the person eating peas is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | drama     | horror     | adventure      | family | martial-arts      | time-travel     |
| Food   | radish | pepper | plum | pumpkin | peas | tomato | corn |

