.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
There 7 different types of food: cabbage, peas, avocado, zucchini, kiwi, lettuce, kale
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: april, may, july, october, december, august, february
 1. the person eating peas is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person eating kale##1
 8. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 9. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Food   | peas | avocado | lettuce     | zucchini | kale | kiwi | cabbage |
| Birthday     | february   | july    | december | august     | april         | october     | may        |

