.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There 7 different types of food: lettuce, broccoli, orange, pineapple, cucumber, pepper, artichoke
7 different games are played: scrabble, domino, billiard, bridge, snooker, canasta, monopoly
 1. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 2. the person eating lettuce is the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 6. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
 7. the person eating pineapple is in the middle##1
 8. the person eating orange is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
10. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Food    | orange | pepper   | lettuce | pineapple | artichoke  | cucumber | broccoli |
| Game   | bridge   | snooker | scrabble | canasta     | domino | monopoly | billiard   |

