.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: sunflower, dahlia, marigold, balloon-flower, iris, begonia, daffodil
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, tea, almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, milk
 1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 3. the person who growsdaffodil is the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 5. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person drinking cola is the person who growsmarigold##1
 8. the person who growsiris is in the middle##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
10. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Flower   | sunflower  | daffodil | balloon-flower | iris | begonia     | dahlia | marigold |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate | coffee      | milk | almond-milk    | iced-tea | tea   | cola  |

