.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: zombie, adventure, superhero, thriller, comedy, time-travel, action
7 different pets are kept: fish, mouse, goat, rat, hedgehog, lizard, hamster
 1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
 3. the person watching adventure movies is the owner of the goat##1
 4. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is the owner of the rat##1
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Movie-Genre       | adventure   | thriller | action | time-travel | zombie     | superhero | comedy |
| Pet   | goat | lizard      | fish        | hamster         | mouse | rat     | hedgehog |

