.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: soccer, climbing, cricket, skiing, surfing, weightlifting, basketball
The people have 7 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, dressmaker, security-guard, manager, police-officer, chef
 1. the manager is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 2. the security-guard is on the right of the police-officer##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 4. the architect is in the middle##1
 5. the security-guard is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 6. the manager is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 8. the architect is on the left of the manager##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the dressmaker is on the right of the firefighter##1
11. the firefighter is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
| Sport        | climbing | soccer | cricket | skiing     | weightlifting | basketball | surfing |
| Job   | police-officer | security-guard  | chef    | architect | manager | firefighter       | dressmaker   |

