.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-13::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: tram, helicopter, scooter, trike, quad-bike, subway, train
City: venice, new-york, paris, hamburg, marseilles, berlin, london
 1. the person traveling to new-york is the person driving the scooter##1
 2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 3. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is the person driving the helicopter##1
 9. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person driving the tram is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
| Transport         | subway | helicopter   | train | tram | quad-bike | trike | scooter  |
| City   | hamburg  | marseilles | london  | paris | berlin | venice     | new-york |

